  "text": "We excluded singletons with missing values on gestational age (mainly singletons born in the years 1978-1981); however, the occurrence of maternal thyroid disease was similar in this group compared to other singletons born in the same period of time and the risk of selection bias due to this exclusion is low, as previously described in detail [CITATION_1] .",
